data.description: Situated on a large, flat lot that backing to the Treynor Golf Course and Recreation Area - enjoy your view from the large deck overlooking the green.  This spacious tri-level in Treynor boasts polished hardwood floors in the kitchen, dining, living, and all upper bedrooms, updated lighting, fresh paint & newer appliances.  One non-conforming bedroom and a ¾ bath in the basement.  Walking distance to elementary school and just 19 minutes from Metro Shopping Center in Council Bluffs. Enjoy small town living close to the city!
